    "description": "你和你率领的一群流浪蟾蜍正在寻找一个可以定居和发展的地方，但却受到了主管死亡的神灵“萨梅迪男爵”的欺骗，被困在了被诅咒的长沼，不得不面对盘踞在这里的邪恶势力。蟾蜍们决心战胜这个可怕的萨梅迪男爵，必须团结起来打败他的一波波爪牙，在长沼建立定居点。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190400/extras/bdd3544038479210fc7b61e74ab3066f.avif?t=1732010153\" width=604 height=104 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190400/extras/4d7ade58787199c01c4395a3161a9b6b.poster.avif?t=1732010153\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190400/extras/4d7ade58787199c01c4395a3161a9b6b.webm?t=1732010153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>管理你的资源以发展你的定居点，扩大你在长沼的蟾蜍数量。所有的建筑，如：驻军、女巫小屋、军械库等，都会有盟友居住，他们会给予你独特的能力和卡牌，以添加到你的卡组。设置陷阱和升级你的领地，以击退攻击你定居点的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190400/extras/c6740917f458cade943753d1219a55bd.avif?t=1732010153\" width=604 height=104 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190400/extras/39527c9ca09661813beb2d077de516a4.poster.avif?t=1732010153\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190400/extras/39527c9ca09661813beb2d077de516a4.webm?t=1732010153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>以网格为基础进行战斗，控制不同的蟾蜍，每只蟾蜍都有自己的特性、优点和弱点。通过程序生成的地图、遭遇战和永久的死亡，每次游戏都是独一无二的，并在每次游戏结束时给予你升级。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190400/extras/361a7d8ddea6ceab6afdc1ed86f8e5ea.avif?t=1732010153\" width=604 height=104 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190400/extras/5ea5be3b86f2922792c4449b9d81675d.poster.avif?t=1732010153\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2190400/extras/5ea5be3b86f2922792c4449b9d81675d.webm?t=1732010153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>将各种战术移动卡牌与强大的战斗卡牌相结合，创造出最强的卡组，以便有效地击败男爵的势力。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Toads of the Bayou包括 :</h2><strong>- 50多张卡牌<br>- 3只可玩的蟾蜍，每只都有不同的能力和特性 <br>- 13座建筑 <br>- 10个头目<br>- 原声音乐</strong>",
